    "However, to our knowledge, no study so far has combined LLMs with AI obfuscation systems, which are supposed to make AI-generated texts undetectable, in the context of scientific experiments.",
    "Thus, our final two research questions were:",
    "RQ7: What criteria are participants using to distinguish text generated by an AI from that written by a human?",
    "RQ8: Is Undetectable.AI able to overcome AI detection systems?",
    "Participants have many legitimate reasons for participating in online studies, which include earning money, satisfying curiosity, and even for entertainment."
